WEBVTT

00:00:29.200 --> 00:00:32.576
And from my name they probably
assume that I'm a Hindu.

00:00:32.600 --> 00:00:34.560
And this sort of fixes me for them.

00:00:36.440 --> 00:00:38.456
But what about the Christians

00:00:38.480 --> 00:00:41.776
and the Muslims and the atheists

00:00:41.800 --> 00:00:43.296
that I grew up with?

00:00:43.320 --> 00:00:45.816
Or the socialists and the liberals,

00:00:45.840 --> 00:00:48.416
even the occasional Tory?

00:00:48.440 --> 00:00:49.456
(Laughter)

00:00:49.480 --> 00:00:51.296
Indeed, all kinds of women and men --

00:00:51.320 --> 00:00:54.256
vegetable sellers, factory workers,
cooks, car mechanics --

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:56.776
living in my working class area,

00:00:56.800 --> 00:00:59.336
in some profoundly important way,

00:00:59.360 --> 00:01:01.056
they are also a part of me